{"tid":2028730,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得國安法可能只係煙慕","createTime":"2020-05-22T03:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T07:58:11.000Z","uid":175033,"like":418,"dislike":111,"uniUserReply":85,"replies":[{"pid":"eca8ade5bc89560256c3e26e0acea1845d8664ca","tid":2028730,"uid":175033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:09:08.000Z","msg":"有冇人覺得共匪係想用國安法帶走國歌法二讀嘅輿論同關注?<br />\n<br />\n相較之下國歌法好似不值一提 過唔過都無所謂 只要經過立法會程序 好過人大憲法<br />\n<br />\n記得魯迅對支那人嘅批評：<br />\n<strong>中國人的性情是總喜歡調和，折中的。譬如你說，這屋子太暗，須在這裏開一個窗，大家一定不允許的。但如果你主張拆掉屋頂，他們就會來調和，願意開窗了。沒有更激烈的主張，他們總連平和的改革也不肯行。</strong><br />\n<br />\n幾值得思考"},{"pid":"55235df0bc740826484751e181ffce4172d51dc2","tid":2028730,"uid":253978,"like":110,"dislike":32,"score":78,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:09:33.000Z","msg":"諗多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b1d422d1aacbeac84cb4014ebdf248bf42bc97","tid":2028730,"uid":175033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:09:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f13c89853a1b1a782b193df5adc1d0c44ed3985","tid":2028730,"uid":175033,"like":69,"dislike":16,"score":53,"quote":{"pid":"55235df0bc740826484751e181ffce4172d51dc2","tid":2028730,"uid":253978,"like":110,"dislike":32,"score":78,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:09:33.000Z","msg":"諗多咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:10:09.000Z","msg":"屌你咁撚早開工"},{"pid":"5495f24bb313e0bce86c1bc4482e844918393a43","tid":2028730,"uid":175033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:10:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"65f65d66a56d4226a785f32fea217f8d6d5c7213","tid":2028730,"uid":175033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:10:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"044f291945f145b34587b35792e7d21fbbb8c46e","tid":2028730,"uid":27146,"like":39,"dislike":3,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T03:10:54.000Z","msg":"本來好多人都話國歌法無力感好重又唔想送頭，不如由佢過喎，呢家....